==English==

===Etymology===
Born out of a typo on qwerty keyboards due to the proximity of the keys “p” and “o.”

===Verb===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-verb}}

# {{italbrac|internet slang|originally [[leet]]}} to [[own]] in the sense of [[defeat]]. Pronounced pōn, poon, own.

